reviewText: Dvd plays well, arrived quickly. You do fine work. Thank you!
I buy movies and cartoons for my family and grandkids based on the story line and the message the movie is trying to convey.  This is a great one that is thought provoking.
We really tried to watch this but the sound was so bad, it couldn't be understood at all.
Just to warn people who may be buying this item thinking it is a film or TV Drama version of the book BE WARNED. It is only a cheap cartoon version.
